    org.springframework.hateoas.Identifiable<Long>

    @Entity
public class User
extends TimedAnnotatableSourcedBE
implements org.springframework.hateoas.Identifiable<Long>
    A User is uniquely identified by a source_id,username pair. Neither source_id nor username alone are unique. However, source_id and username are unique in the context of a given Discourse. TODO: We should make sure that source_id and username each are unique within a certain Discourse context
    Author:
    Oliver Ferschke
